Lo and behold Ellis visited
that same location

31:29.889 --> 31:32.322
    of the shooting 16 times
   over the last four years.

31:32.324 --> 31:34.391
- So we ran everyone
that was arrested in the area

31:34.393 --> 31:38.462
    - Could you just tell us
    what you found, please?

31:38.464 --> 31:41.365
        - Dewan Motley.
     - Who's Dewan Motley?

31:41.367 --> 31:44.067
            - May I?

31:44.069 --> 31:45.969
      He was a live-in boyfriend

31:45.971 --> 31:48.005
         of one of Ellis' aunts.

31:50.041 --> 31:53.577
Basically, a whole lot went down
            between Dewan Motley

31:53.579 --> 31:57.281
          and the CPD
  at this exact same location

31:57.283 --> 32:00.083
         six years ago.

32:00.085 --> 32:02.119
   I'll keep digging around.

32:02.121 --> 32:03.520
         See if anyone
       close to Motley--

32:03.522 --> 32:04.988
                       - No, no.
          Thanks for coming down

32:04.990 --> 32:07.424
                and briefing us.
   Intelligence has to stay away

32:07.426 --> 32:08.692
         at this point.
         - How's that?

32:08.694 --> 32:10.394
               - Green's running
      a reasonable doubt defense

32:10.396 --> 32:11.995
         and she's gonna bury us
                  if we give her

32:11.997 --> 32:14.097
  anymore conflicts of interest.

32:16.267 --> 32:18.368
- You gonna be able
to close on this, kid?

32:19.604 --> 32:21.505
              - I think you know
             I'm able, Sergeant.

32:22.573 --> 32:25.575
- Except when you
put me away

32:25.577 --> 32:28.111
you had this, kind of,
world-beater look in your eye.

32:28.113 --> 32:29.546
I'm not seeing it
right now, Peter.

32:29.548 --> 32:32.582
- That's because the case on you
                was a slam dunk.

32:39.023 --> 32:40.991
- That look.

32:44.095 --> 32:47.197
 [crowd chanting indistinctly]

32:49.701 --> 32:52.703
